# =============================================================================
# Testing Headers
# =============================================================================
#
# Use these tools to verify your headers are configured correctly:
#
# 1. Browser DevTools -> Network -> Response Headers
# 2. https://securityheaders.com/
# 3. https://observatory.mozilla.org/
#
# To test SharedArrayBuffer availability:
# Open console and run: console.log(typeof SharedArrayBuffer)
# Should return "function" if cross-origin isolation is working.
#
# To test crossOriginIsolated:
# Open console and run: window.crossOriginIsolated
# Should return true.
